                                      variable:
-> variable is name which can store a value byt there are some ruls which we have to follow
->{variable ek name (koi bhi name ho sakta hai)jo value store karta hai }

->variable is devide in 3 steps:
(1)variable declaration
(2)variable initialization
(3)variable colling or variable use

(1) variable declaration:
-> before use with variable we must declare with spacific datatype
->{variable ka use karne se pehle hame usse btana hoga ki vo kis datatype ko store karega}

syntaxt:<datatype> variable

(2) variable initlization:
-> assign a value
-> {jo bhi value ho vo kikho}
syntext: varoable = value

(3) variable use

syntext:  printf("<datatype>",variable)
