                                                           for loop
(1)for loop
-> for loop is sequence controlled loop
{ jab hamko numbers pta ho ki kaha se kaha tak loop karna ho}

for loop is devided in 3 counter

syntex:
for(counter1;counter2;counter3)
{

}

syntex:
for(initialization;condition;updation)
{

}
